org.apache.activemq.core.server

Class ActiveMQServers

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.activemq.core.server.ActiveMQServers

  • public final class ActiveMQServers
extends Object
    ActiveMQServers is a factory class for instantiating ActiveMQServer instances.

    This class should be used when you want to instantiate a ActiveMQServer instance for embedding in your own application, as opposed to directly instantiating an implementing instance.

    Author:
    Tim Fox
